  <description><![CDATA[<p>The recently renovated Braubär Hotel is a stylish hotel, previously known as the Alpine Hotel Wengen or Sunstar Wengen. It's been lovingly transformed yet maintains a traditional feel with a relaxed and friendly atmosphere.</p>
<h2>Chic, centrally located hotel</h2>
<p>With its position in the centre of Wengen, directly across from the Männlichen lift and only a short walk from Wengen station, you'll be perfectly located for discovering all the Jungfrau region has to offer. The food is excellent and you can book Bed and Breakfast or Half Board - perhaps treat yourself to a unique evening in the Fondue Gondola in the garden (payable locally).</p>
<h2>Luxurious NUXE Spa</h2>
<p>When you're done exploring and ready to relax - the NUXE Spa is just the place. Relax and enjoy the view on the wellness terrace, treat yourself to a sauna session, or head inside to the indoor swimming pool and steam room. Massages and beauty treatments are available to book locally, too.</p>
<p>Round off your day in the hotel's cosy bar, with good music and a great menu of wine, cocktails and refreshing, long drinks.</p>]]></description>
